nodes.text: Winston Wolff has worked on several LucasArts titles. He worked on the first two titles in the Dark Forces Saga, Star Wars: Dark Forces and credited for level editor, user interface and tools on Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II. He also worked on Star Wars: DroidWorks and Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire, other LucasArts titles includes Grim Fandango, Outlaws, Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine and Full Throttle.
